item.description:
@gpunks15 wrote:

ha im no pro but as for the java error you fixed it with the Programs (x86) thing so thats good now for your second pic. Your cache is gone or not in the right spot, as you say it said :Data/cache/main faile blah blah. So you must make a folder named “cache” in the “Data” folder in your source. and place all your cache files in there. I’m guessing this is a 711 server. if i knew i would be able to help more. Hope this helped a bit.
